{{Tree chart| ||!| | | |!| | | | ,| -|^|- |.|}}
{{Tree chart| |Koutou | | ME  |y | SIS | |SHIN|y|YAYA| |Koutou=Imperial Family Line|ME=Takeiwatatsu no Mikoto|SIS=Asotsuhime no Mikoto|SHIN=Shinhiko no Mikoto|YAYA=Yahime no Kami |}}
