{{Tree chart| |||MOM| y| DAD|| | | DAISY |MOM=Wakahime no Kami|DAD=Hikomiko no Kami|DAISY=Aso Shrine Extended Family}}
{{Tree chart| ||| | ||!|}}
{{Tree chart| | | | | | MOM|MOM=''Current'' Aso Shrine Priests}}
{{Tree chart/end}}<ref>{{Cite book |last1=Takano |first1=Tomoaki |title=History and Festivals of the Aso Shrine |last2=Uchimura |first2=Hiroaki |publisher=Aso Shrine |year=2006 |location=Aso Shrine, Ichinomiya, Aso City.}}</ref>

== See also ==

* [[Hikoyai|Hikoyai-mo-mikoto]] (彦八井耳命) - Some say that he was the brother, son, or the same person as {{Interlanguage link|Kamuyaimimi|lt=Kamuyaimimi|ja|神八井耳命}}. Some also believe that he is the national dragon god enshrined at [[Aso Shrine]].

